Debugging Terraform Issues:

Investigating unexpected terraform behaviour
Preparing bug reports for hashicorp team
Understanding what exactly terraform is doing under the hood.

TF_LOG Env Variable:
Setting TF_LOG enables detailed monitoring
export TF_LOG=TRACE
$terraform plan

Separate Core and provider logging:
TF_LOG_CORE=TRACE
TF_LOG_PROVIDER=TRACE

Saving logs to a file : 
Persist logs using the TF_LOG_PATH env
export TF_LOG-TRACE
export TF_LOG_PATH=terraform.log
